title: Let’s Talk About Pokemon - Bouffalant
body:
626: Bouffalant

A plenty appropriate Pokemon to introduce for a North American region. A pretty obvious parallel to Tauros too. To a point where people also thought this was gonna be Tauros’s evolved form. But yeah, just like Tauros, this… sure is a buffalo. One with an afro, for some reason. But a buffalo nonetheless.

Personal Score: 5.5/10

Not much to say besides that.

summary: Pokemon Let's Go games are frickin from what we've seen, are just made for toddlers. Like it's one thing to have gym battle...
body: Pokemon Let’s Go games are frickin from what we’ve seen, are just made for toddlers. Like it’s one thing to have gym battle restrictions, but to literally take out wild battles and make puzzles straight up easier than beginner?? Like if you ask the Pokemon Go players, they don’t give a shit about this game?? I don’t care if I’m gonna get anon hate for being negative about this game by the Pokemon-blind-worshipper stans on Tumblr. This game shouldn’t be 60 dollars.

summary: Mega Rayquarizard Mega Rayquaza, Mega Charizard X and Mega Charizard Y fusion Fire/Dragon Type Ability: Legendary Dragon -...
caption:
Mega Rayquarizard

Mega Rayquaza, Mega Charizard X and Mega Charizard Y fusion

Fire/Dragon Type

Ability: Legendary Dragon - Rayquarizard is immune to ground type attacks as it levitates and gains a 1.5x boost to super effective attacks.

Stats: HP - 100, Atk - 150, Def - 105, SpA - 170, SpD - 105, Spe - 120

Moveset: Fire Blast, Draco Meteor, Stone Edge, Earthquake

The Volcanic Dragon Pokemon

When Rayquarizard Mega Evolves, its flames burn hotter and brighter.  It can withstand very high temperatures and can even keep itself warm in the coldest environments by melting its surroundings.  Only the bravest of trainers can see its magnificent mega form.  Loosing is never an option for it.

Part 2 request for @flylng-sausage. I hope you like it.  I just wanted to make a bigger dragon.  Big noodle dragon.  Very fiery noodle.  A good magnificent boy.  And with a mega stone as well.
